《'''Hush'''》（{{韓|諺='''허쉬'''}}），為[[韓國|韓國]][[JTBC|JTBC]]於2020年12月11日起播出的[[JTBC金土連續劇|金土連續劇]]，改編自鄭振永的2018年小說《沉默警報》，由《[[獨酒男女|獨酒男女]]》崔奎植導演與《[[Suits_(韓國電視劇)|金裝律師]]》金正敏編劇合作打造。此劇講述拿起台球棍比筆的日子更多的「古董」記者，與覺得飯比筆更強大的「生存型」實習記者的雙方成長記，以及月薪族記者們的賺錢生活。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125382|title=少女時代「潤娥」確定出演 JTBC 全新職場劇《Hush》挑戰熱血女記者|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-03-25|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024020754/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125382|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Jessica|url=https://www.kpopn.com/2020/10/14/hwang-jung-min-yoona-new-drama-confirm-broadcast-in-december|title=黃正民暌違八年回歸小螢幕，與潤娥合作新劇定檔12月|publisher=Kpopn|date=2020-10-14|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024062155/https://www.kpopn.com/2020/10/14/hwang-jung-min-yoona-new-drama-confirm-broadcast-in-december|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131297|title=[有片]《HUSH》第一波Teaser公開！黄晸玟＋林潤娥演出為月薪奔波的記者們生活日常|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-10-30|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126180605/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131297|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131401|title=黃晸玟&潤娥主演笑中帶淚職場劇《Hush》公開人物海報上熱搜！|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-11-04|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104132803/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131401|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131846|title=《Hush》最新劇照公開：黃晸玟＋潤娥＝資深記者與菜鳥記者的對比|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-11-23|language=zh-hant|accessdate=2020-12-12|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108201700/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131846|dead-url=no}}</ref>

